msgctxt "sn45.37:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 45 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 45 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.37:0.2"
msgid "4. Paṭipattivagga "
msgstr "4. Practice "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn45.37:0.3"
msgid "37. Paṭhamabrahmaññasutta "
msgstr "37. The Brahmin Life (1st) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.26, sc1
msgctxt "sn45.37:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.37:1.2"
msgid "“Brahmaññañca vo, bhikkhave, desessāmi, brahmaññaphalāni ca. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, I will teach you life as a brahmin and the fruits of life as a brahmin. "

msgctxt "sn45.37:1.3"
msgid "Taṃ suṇātha. "
msgstr "Listen … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.37:1.4"
msgid "Katamañca kho, bhikkhave, brahmaññaṃ? "
msgstr "And what is life as a brahmin? "

msgctxt "sn45.37:1.5"
msgid "Ayameva ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo, seyyathidaṃ—"
msgstr "It is simply this noble eightfold path, that is: "

msgctxt "sn45.37:1.6"
msgid "sammādiṭṭhi … pe … sammāsamādhi. "
msgstr "right view, right thought, right speech, right action, right livelihood, right effort, right mindfulness, and right immersion. "

msgctxt "sn45.37:1.7"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, brahmaññaṃ. "
msgstr "This is called life as a brahmin. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.37:1.8"
msgid "Katamāni ca, bhikkhave, brahmaññaphalāni? "
msgstr "And what are the fruits of life as a brahmin? "

msgctxt "sn45.37:1.9"
msgid "Sotāpattiphalaṃ, sakadāgāmiphalaṃ, anāgāmiphalaṃ, arahattaphalaṃ—"
msgstr "The fruits of stream-entry, once-return, non-return, and perfection. "

msgctxt "sn45.37:1.10"
msgid "imāni vuccanti, bhikkhave, brahmaññaphalānī”ti. "
msgstr "These are called the fruits of life as a brahmin.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.37:1.11"
msgid "Sattamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
